entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found Trehla, she should be able to help you understand what to do a little better.
entries.journal_entry_description: You've received a waypoint to Trehla. Find the blue shaft of light and head towards it.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Trehla should be able to help you with Mos Eisley and some of the game. Go see her if you need more instruction.
